    services: 'Your customs broker license is your livelihood—aggressive defense protects it from CBP enforcement actions and client litigation. We defend against license revocation proceedings, civil penalties under 19 U.S.C. § 1641, and responsible supervision allegations. Our team prepares reinstatement applications, responds to Broker Management Branch investigations, drafts protective Powers of Attorney limiting liability exposure from importer negligence, represents brokers in surety disputes, and defends against importer lawsuits alleging professional negligence. Protecting your license, reputation, and business assets is our priority. Call immediately upon receiving CBP enforcement notices or client litigation threats.',
